author: stsp
msg: Move defintion of relpath_depth() helper function from wc_db.c into the
wc_db_private.h header file. This allows relpath_depth() to be used in
other wc_db files without duplicate implementations. The function is static
and thus doesn't need an svn_ prefix to avoid API namespace pollution.
(relpath_depth_sqlite): ... this to avoid collision with the relpath_depth()
